### Railway PostgreSQL 部署測試

# 1. 檢查 API 狀態
GET https://japaneseflashcardapi-production.up.railway.app/

###

# 2. 獲取所有單字卡（測試資料庫連線）
GET https://japaneseflashcardapi-production.up.railway.app/api/flashcards

###

# 3. 新增一張測試單字卡（驗證資料持久化）
POST https://japaneseflashcardapi-production.up.railway.app/api/flashcards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "japaneseText": "テスト",
  "hiragana": "てすと",
  "englishTranslation": "test",
  "difficulty": 1,
  "tags": ["測試", "Railway", "PostgreSQL"]
}

###

# 4. 再次獲取所有單字卡（確認新資料已保存）
GET https://japaneseflashcardapi-production.up.railway.app/api/flashcards

###

# 5. 測試批量匯入
